how to start a new line in posit
ChatGPT 说：
ChatGPT
In Posit Cloud (RStudio), starting a new line within code or text follows these simple rules:

Within Code: Press Enter to start a new line.

This works in both R scripts (.R) and in R Markdown (.Rmd) or Quarto (.qmd) code chunks.
In Markdown Text:

For a single line break, add two spaces at the end of a line, then press Enter.
For a new paragraph, simply press Enter twice to create a blank line between paragraphs.
In Inline Code Blocks or Text:

When writing inline code or text that needs line breaks for readability, use <br> in Markdown or Quarto documents:
markdown
复制代码
This is line one. <br> This is line two.
This should help format your content effectively within Posit Cloud!